RTE:
When using the line break before a table, the escape character is inserted in the table heading.

So:
{noformat}
\\ || Column A || Column B ||
| Quality Center | Excel |
{noformat}
becomes:
{noformat}
\\
\|\| Column A \|\| Column B \|\|
| Quality Center | Excel |
{noformat}

