Although it is possible to subscribe to multiple individual calendars to make a new calendar, it is not possible to then take that consolidated calendar and subscribe to it from another calendar. 

We have a situation where multiple employees have personal vacation calendars which we consolidate into a single calendar.  We would then like to subscribe to the vacation calendar from our work plan calendar.  Unfortunately, this is not currently possible such that if we have a new employee that we would otherwise just add to the vacation calendar and expect it to be updated everywhere, we have to go to each of the calendars individually that have employee vacations on them and add the new calendar individually.

